### 
# POST {{base}}/auth/register
# Content-Type: application/json

# { "displayName": "admin tester 1", "phone": "08020000000", "password": "testpass123" }

# ### 
# POST {{base}}/auth/login
# X-Session-Id: ses_test_2
# Content-Type: application/json

# { "phone": "08031234567", "password": "testpass123" }


### 1. flag a price (user A) -> 201, flagCount 1, status ACTIVE
POST {{base}}/prices/{{submissionId}}/flag
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "reason": "WRONG_PRICE" }

### 2. same user again -> 409 "already reported"
POST {{base}}/prices/{{submissionId}}/flag
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "reason": "WRONG_PRICE" }

### 3. user B flags -> flagCount 2, still ACTIVE
POST {{base}}/prices/{{submissionId}}/flag
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenB}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "reason": "WRONG_PRICE" }

### 4. user C flags -> flagCount 3, status UNDER_REVIEW
POST {{base}}/prices/{{submissionId}}/flag
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenC}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "reason": "OUTDATED" }

### 5. that price is now GONE from compare and the feed
GET {{base}}/markets/compare?itemId={{riceId}}&unitId={{dericaId}}

### 6. admin sees it in the queue
GET {{base}}/admin/moderation
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. non-admin hits admin -> 403
GET {{base}}/admin/moderation
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

### 8. admin restores it -> back to ACTIVE, flags DISMISSED
PATCH {{base}}/admin/moderation/{{submissionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "action": "RESTORE" }

### 9. market request -> 201 PENDING
POST {{base}}/market-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "proposedName": "Rumuokoro Market", "lga": "Obio/Akpor", "state": "Rivers" }

### 10. duplicate request -> 409
POST {{base}}/market-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "proposedName": "Rumuokoro Market", "lga": "Obio/Akpor", "state": "Rivers" }

### 11. GET /market-requests/mine -> your request
GET {{base}}/market-requests/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

### 12. admin approves -> creates a Market
PATCH {{base}}/admin/market-requests/{{requestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "action": "APPROVE" }

### 13. GET /markets now includes Rumuokoro
GET {{base}}/markets